763
00:57:30,579 --> 00:57:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] njegovi zemlji ostace danas čuvaju

764
00:57:32,599 --> 00:57:34,340
[SPEAKER_00] staklenom sarkofagu u Franjevačkom

765
00:57:34,340 --> 00:57:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] samostanu u Jajcu,

766
00:57:35,340 --> 00:57:38,320
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije dorastao težini trenutka.

767
00:57:38,320 --> 00:57:40,719
[SPEAKER_00] I on je doista vjerovao

768
00:57:40,719 --> 00:57:41,659
[SPEAKER_00] da će pomoć,

769
00:57:41,659 --> 00:57:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] ta verbalizirana pomoć

770
00:57:44,380 --> 00:57:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] Zapadne Evrope, predvođena prije svega

771
