775
00:57:55,579 --> 00:57:56,920
[SPEAKER_00] ali ta pomoć je zapravo

776
00:57:56,920 --> 00:57:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] izostala.

777
00:57:59,079 --> 00:58:01,780
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva Svete Marije

778
00:58:01,780 --> 00:58:04,360
[SPEAKER_00] sa zvonikom Svjetoga Luke

779
00:58:04,360 --> 00:58:06,059
[SPEAKER_00] je Stjepan Tomašević

780
00:58:06,059 --> 00:58:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] krunisan, jedini bosanski vladar

781
00:58:08,039 --> 00:58:08,820
