833
00:59:42,179 --> 00:59:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] Može sljedeća.

834
00:59:43,539 --> 00:59:46,260
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to je zapravo

835
00:59:46,260 --> 00:59:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] sarkofag Stjepana Tomaševića

836
00:59:47,880 --> 00:59:49,760
