901
01:01:46,340 --> 01:01:47,719
[SPEAKER_00] U tome nije uspjela,

902
01:01:47,719 --> 01:01:48,619
[SPEAKER_00] umrla je u Rimu

903
01:01:48,619 --> 01:01:50,639
[SPEAKER_00] 1678. godine,

904
01:01:50,639 --> 01:01:53,219
[SPEAKER_00] toliko želeći se vratiti

905
01:01:53,219 --> 01:01:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo u Bosnu.

906
01:01:54,599 --> 01:01:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] Njezine kosti i dan danas

907
01:01:56,500 --> 01:01:57,900
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo počivaju daleko

908
